The staff kept telling me I was next and there was no real indication of when I would be seen. If the dr makes his patients wait that long it‚Äôs really upsetting ! We have lives and our time is precious, don‚Äôt overbook urself and make people wait all day it‚Äôs terrible. Not to mention I have another 40 min drive home.

I ended up walking out because I simply couldn‚Äôt take it anymore. I refuse to pay for a dermatologist to see me when I can go any place and spend less of my life waiting on someone. Don‚Äôt bother coming to this terrible place unless you want to really WASTE your time.
